        A <b>Point_sequence</b> is a type of
        <express_ref linkend="elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Detailed_geometric_model_element"/>
        that represents an ordered lists of points.
</ext_description>

<ext_description linkend="Point_direction_model_arm.Point_sequence.items">
	specifies the point elements that define the consecutive points.
</ext_description>

